  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join The Discord!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/f5b9911fc1c9eec075770164c929630f.avif?t=1731609190\" width=460 height=102 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/3b445ee4629e94049d32a817ee3826be.avif?t=1731609190\" width=480 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/3810464d1d949548839b4118cec3d465.poster.avif?t=1731609190\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/3810464d1d949548839b4118cec3d465.webm?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/3810464d1d949548839b4118cec3d465.mp4?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Step into the boots of a lone astronaut and defend your base in an immersive third-person tower defense game! Without weapons, rely solely on strategic tower placement and swift maneuvers to fend off waves of relentless enemies targeting you. Each escalating wave promises heart-pounding action and suspense, challenging your survival skills to the limit. Prepare to face hordes of robots, aliens, and RPG style boss fights. Are you ready?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/0d72646426b8271e21573108bfcaa8db.avif?t=1731609190\" width=415 height=103 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/697430ab30e9e78a81ac58f0260a2661.webp?t=1731609190\" width=328 height=39 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/a8cf36b910ed4da89d3143066a47db5b.poster.avif?t=1731609190\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/a8cf36b910ed4da89d3143066a47db5b.webm?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/a8cf36b910ed4da89d3143066a47db5b.mp4?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The player has no weapon. Instead, build turrets around the arena to defeat the incoming waves of enemies. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/34c234227f86e60bf8ab705ece4cf32d.webp?t=1731609190\" width=272 height=41 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/a2ef5f95dc6ae0ceb4cf6e48a4c0fac0.poster.avif?t=1731609190\" width=480 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/a2ef5f95dc6ae0ceb4cf6e48a4c0fac0.webm?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/a2ef5f95dc6ae0ceb4cf6e48a4c0fac0.mp4?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>Each level uses unique turrets that fit the theme of the environment and have unique abilities. All will be needed to ensure victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/7a6fcec20e217c016137ff0dcb82d994.webp?t=1731609190\" width=326 height=41 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/f3e33bbd9ddd1f50e834ebe27b489524.poster.avif?t=1731609190\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/f3e33bbd9ddd1f50e834ebe27b489524.webm?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/f3e33bbd9ddd1f50e834ebe27b489524.mp4?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Scour the arena for traps and items to pick up and use against your enemies. These range from bombs, stun traps, slow fields, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/1b38b0c09566b5a34d9c41bc034191d1.webp?t=1731609190\" width=255 height=40 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/d1e2e38f559c4c6c0ddeb6669b02fbb1.poster.avif?t=1731609190\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/d1e2e38f559c4c6c0ddeb6669b02fbb1.webm?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864230/extras/d1e2e38f559c4c6c0ddeb6669b02fbb1.mp4?t=1731609190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Encounter unique, RPG style boss fights where the player must balance their play between building up a strong turret defense, dodging enemy abilities, and achieving necessary goals to obtain victory.",
